<td valign="top"><font size = "3">XY LC</font></td>
<td><italic>A mode of play where all Pokemon are set to Level 5. Only Pokemon that can evolve and are not evolved from anything can participate.</italic><br /><br />
<span style="font-weight:bold">Banned Pokemon:</span> Scyther, Tangela, Sneasel, Gligar, Yanma<br /><br/>
