<td valign="top"><font size = "3">XY <br/>Monotype</font></td>
<td><italic>A mode of play where all Pokemon on a team must share a common type.</italic><br /><br />
<span style="font-weight:bold">Banned Items:</span> Soul Dew<br/><br/>
<span style="font-weight:bold">Banned Pokemon:</span> Arceus, Blaziken, Darkrai, Deoxys-A, Deoxys-S, Deoxys-N, Dialga, Giratina, Giratina-O, Groudon, Ho-oh, Kyogre, Kyurem-W, Lugia, Mewtwo, Palkia, Rayquaza, Reshiram, Shaymin-S, Xerneas, Yveltal, Zekrom<br /><br/>
</td>
</tr><tr>
<td valign="top"><font size = "3">Inverted Battle</font></td>
<td><italic>A mode of play where all Type Effectivenesses are inverted (Ex: Water is weak to Fire)</italic><br /><br />
<span style="font-weight:bold">Banned Items:</span> Soul Dew, Kangaskhanite, Gengarite<br /><br />
<span style="font-weight:bold">Banned Pokemon:</span> Arceus, Darkrai, Deoxys-A, Deoxys-N, Dialga, Giratina, Giratina-O, Groudon, Ho-oh, Kyogre, Kyurem-B, Kyurem-W, Lugia, Mewtwo, Palkia, Rayquaza, Reshiram, Shaymin-S, Xerneas, Yveltal, Zekrom<br/><br/>
</td>
</tr><tr>
<td valign="top"><font size = "3">Sky Battle</font></td>
